  @contract  skips non-note plans/cols; optional `deleted` event-set excluded from the walk  @ 316
  @invariant  deleted corpses still live in col.events snapshot until next rebuild  @ 317
  @invariant  a freshly placed note is unbounded: endppq = util.OPEN, no authored ceiling  @ 768
  @invariant  universal tail pass derives the real tail (next onset/take length) each rebuild  @ 769
  @contract  caller pre-pins (ppq, ppqL, rpb) onto `update` before calling  @ 770
  @contract  col nil only for a chord sprout (no column yet): no prev-vel to inherit, lane pre-set  @ 771
