  @contract  arms on a note col's first pitch stop; pins (row, chan) until shift release  @ 1116
  @contract  returns true iff consumed; false lets the drain fall through (to value-digit entry)  @ 1117
  @contract  re-striking a gesture pitch toggles it off; freed slots are reused lowest-first  @ 1118
  @contract  spreadChan strikes walk channels up from home; plain strikes stack home-channel lanes  @ 1119
  @invariant  pins (col,row,part); overwrites a place keep-below, steps the sub-caret right  @ 1237
  @invariant  field re-read via cells[row] each keystroke; undo snapshots drive backspace-restore  @ 1238
  @contract  selection must be exactly one grid column; multi-col selection is a no-op  @ 2714
  @invariant  a 1-col block stays contiguous when it lands on the destination col  @ 2715
  @contract  cursor follows to the destination column (single event and selection alike)  @ 2716
  @contract  refuse if dest col has any onset in source's row extent (note: note-on; else any event)  @ 2717
  @invariant  source's row extent = selection's [r1,r2] for a block, moved event's onset row for a single  @ 2718
  @invariant  tails (either direction) clipped by tm's tail pass; never block  @ 2719
  @contract  reentrancy-guarded; bails on no-take (page shows placeholder)  @ 3655
  @contract  takeChanged=true resets ec and re-reads resolution/length/timeSigs  @ 3656
  @contract  grid + ctx rebuild each call; pushMute at end  @ 3657
